com.tymeac.base

Class AreaList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tymeac.base.AreaList

  • public final class AreaList
extends java.lang.Object
    This is just the list of all Tymeac Queues. Built at start-up by adding one entry at a time, it never changes.
